                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">DEAN</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18670128-244-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18670128-244-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670128-244-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy by the Jury, he being much under the influence of Holdsworth.—<rs id="t18670128-244-punishment-49" type="punishmentDescription">
